    "eyebrow": "Lifestyle",
    "num": "05",
    "deck": "<div class=\"wrap\"><div class=\"eyebrow anim\"><span class=\"num\">05</span><span class=\"bar\"></span>Lifestyle</div><h2 class=\"head anim\">Texican Frontier Life</h2><ul><li>Agricultural economy with ranching and farming</li><li>Blended Mexican and Anglo cultural practices</li><li>Faced challenges from Native American tribes and frontier conditions</li></ul><p class=\"lede anim\">Texicans lived a frontier lifestyle combining Mexican traditions like ranching with Anglo farming methods, adapting to challenges such as conflicts and isolation (s8, s9). <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s8\">[8]</sup> <sup class=\"cite\" data-src=\"s9\">[9]</sup></p><div class=\"lesson-detail anim\"><p><strong>Example:</strong> Texican families often celebrated Mexican festivals while adopting Anglo-style homes and farming techniques.</p><p><strong>Practice:</strong> Consider how frontier challenges influenced Texican daily life and culture.</p><p><strong>Watch for:</strong> Overgeneralizing Texican culture as purely Mexican or Anglo.</p></div></div>",
